  "Description": {
    "English": "A highly advanced piece of technology for use in the next generation of power plants. Producing a fusion core requires both intricate scientific skills and complex industrial processes.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Portable Reactor</span>, <span class=\"name name-technology\">Quantum Processors</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">Geodesite</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "极为先进的技术，用于新一代发电站中。生产融合核心需要复杂的科学技术和工业制成。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-fuel\">便携式反应器</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">量子处理器</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">晶土矿</span>制作。",
    "TencentChinese": "极为先进的技术，用于新一代发电站中。生产融合核心需要复杂的科学技术和工业制成。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-fuel\">便携式反应器</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">量子处理器</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">晶土矿</span>制作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "高度先進的科技，專門使用在次世代的發電廠上。製造融合核心不僅需要精密的科學技巧，還要複雜的工業流程。<br><br>可使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">可攜式反應器</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">量子處理器</span>與<span class=\"name name-special\">晶球岩</span>製造。"
  },
